            session_key_id,
            lit_encrypted_keypair_id,
            max_amount_usd,
            expires_at,
            delegation_signature,
            delegation_message,
            created_from_ip,
            created_from_device,
            metadata
        ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
        RETURNING id
